{"tid":376572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗公路奪命車禍　警方：司機戴安全帶仍拋出車外死亡","createTime":"2017-08-27T05:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T09:08:03.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10f793b005d7d03658b70e95a058b319529e022b","tid":376572,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:57:38.000Z","msg":"元朗公路發生奪命車禍，新界北交通特別意外調查隊第一隊何泰然督察交代案件指，今晨6時許，一輛輕型貨車由元朗工業邨出發，前往屯門大興邨方向，駛至元朗工路近菜園村路段，突然失控由第三線撞至第一線防撞欄，男司機被拋出車外，另外兩名傷者分別左腳及左邊頭部受傷，3人送院，當中司機傷重不治，兩名傷者為其女親友及員工。<br />\n<br />\n何表示，相信司機有佩帶安全帶，警方將會循車速、輕型貨車的性能及現場環境3個方向調查車禍原因。"},{"pid":"3cbea35615555b1688ef93b1828c94b8da1b4f67","tid":376572,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:57:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170827/s00001/1503809180912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170827%2Fs00001%2F1503809180912&d=kU30Ydmir2pA2vF7v7OBMk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d1a48b9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170827%2Fs00001%2F1503809180912&h=96e6d146\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170827/s00001/1503809180912</a>"},{"pid":"08634a190c032b2d30a687d44cac5955279c39d9","tid":376572,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:10:21.000Z","msg":"條安全帶用左金錢結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df5860951045ebb2feacd5f66fe131229d73970","tid":376572,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a33259ffc6f8638d89087590b531728ceab272","tid":376572,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:08:03.000Z","msg":"農曆七月啊 rip"}]}